messenger_inbox.text:
 said: "Thanks for the invite. I’m sourcing time‑sensitive goods and will award based on total value: delivered price, freshness/quality guarantees, reliable delivery windows, and after‑sales support. Near‑term need: a pilot this week of ~30 units delivered tomorrow morning (7–9am). If quality is consistent, scale to 60–80 units/week over the next month. 

Could you share: 
- your delivered unit price at 30 units and any price breaks at 60/80; 
- any delivery fees; 
- freshness/quality standards and return/replacem"

